---
title: 정보 개더링 전체 아키텍처 — IP 하나로 멀티벤더 서버 표준 수집
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    fontFamily: 'Pretendard, Malgun Gothic, Noto Sans KR, sans-serif'
    fontSize: '14px'
    primaryTextColor: '#1E293B'
    lineColor: '#64748B'
    edgeLabelBackground: '#FFFFFF'
    clusterBkg: '#F8FAFC'
    clusterBorder: '#CBD5E1'
  flowchart:
    nodeSpacing: 38
    rankSpacing: 60
    padding: 10
---
flowchart LR
  subgraph IN["입력"]
    direction TB
    PORTAL["사내 클라우드 포털<br/>IP 1개 + 대상 종류"]:::input
    PARAM["Job 파라미터<br/>loc(A/B/C), target_type"]:::input
    PORTAL --> PARAM
  end

  subgraph ORCH["Jenkins 4-Stage"]
    direction TB
    ST1["① Validate · 입력 검증"]:::proc
    ST2["② Gather · 채널 실행"]:::proc
    ST3["③ Validate Schema · 정합"]:::proc
    ST4["④ E2E 회귀 / Callback"]:::proc
    ST1 --> ST2 --> ST3 --> ST4
  end

  subgraph CH["점검 — 사전진단 후 3채널 (본체는 제조사 모름)"]
    direction TB
    PRE["사전진단 4단계<br/>ping→port→protocol→auth"]:::gate
    OSG["os-gather · SSH · WinRM"]:::proc
    ESXG["esxi-gather · vSphere"]:::proc
    RFG["redfish-gather · Redfish"]:::proc
    PRE --> OSG
    PRE --> ESXG
    PRE --> RFG
    PRE -.->|"차단 시"| PFAIL["실패 단계 기록"]:::fail
  end

  subgraph NORM["정규화"]
    direction TB
    ADP["adapter 자동 선택<br/>prio×1000+spec×10+match"]:::proc
    FRAG["fragment 누적 병합"]:::proc
    BLD["공통 builder 6종"]:::proc
    ADP --> FRAG --> BLD
  end

  OUT(["출력<br/>13필드 표준 JSON<br/>성공이든 실패든 같은 구조"]):::env

  IN -->|"HTTPS 443"| ORCH
  ORCH -->|"Gather 단계"| CH
  CH -->|"raw 응답"| NORM
  NORM --> OUT
  PFAIL --> OUT

  subgraph BASE["기반 자산 — 이 위에서 동작"]
    direction LR
    VAULT["Ansible Vault<br/>제조사별 자격증명"]:::store
    ADPY["adapter YAML"]:::store
    SCHEMA["schema · baseline"]:::store
    REDIS["Redis fact 캐시"]:::store
  end
  NORM -.->|"Vault · schema · 캐시 참조"| BASE

  subgraph LEGEND["범례"]
    direction LR
    LG1["처리 단계"]:::proc
    LG2["기반 자산"]:::store
    LG3["출력"]:::env
    LG4["실패, 차단"]:::fail
  end
  BASE ~~~ LEGEND

  classDef input fill:#F1F5F9,stroke:#94A3B8,color:#1E293B,stroke-width:1.5px
  classDef proc fill:#EEF2FF,stroke:#6366F1,color:#1E293B,stroke-width:1.5px
  classDef gate fill:#FFFBEB,stroke:#F59E0B,color:#1E293B,stroke-width:1.5px
  classDef store fill:#ECFDF5,stroke:#10B981,color:#1E293B,stroke-width:1.5px
  classDef env fill:#ECFDF5,stroke:#10B981,color:#1E293B,stroke-width:2px
  classDef fail fill:#FFF1F2,stroke:#F43F5E,color:#1E293B,stroke-width:1.5px
